library(tidyverse)
library(readxl)
library(janitor)
library(ggrepel)
url1 <- "https://query.data.world/s/tw3oaknxjlqods27xzzbpa3do4rmfr"
p1f <- tempfile()
download.file(url1, p1f, mode="wb")
happy_data <- read_excel(path = p1f)

Tidying

colnames(happy_data)[4] <- "life_ladder"

data <- clean_names(happy_data) #Cleaning data names

Take 1

data1 <- select(filter(data, year == 2016), "country", "life_ladder", "positive_affect", "negative_affect")
